summary: Imagine being drunk and falling asleep using Harry’s legs as a pillow while he runs his fingers through your hair and whispers...
question: Imagine being drunk and falling asleep using Harry’s legs as a pillow while he runs his fingers through your hair and whispers about how you’re going to be feeling horrible in the morning.
answer:
“tomorrow’s gonna be horrid for you.”

harry amusingly and entertainingly whispers to his love’s ear, all asleep and laid down on his lap while you’re unconsciouslt fisting his shirt.

you may have had a little too much and he may have had a little too less that ended up like this, the both of you on the couch and not even making it to the bed since you’ve practically begged him to just have the both of you sit momentarily.

he’s laughing, eyes crinkling just by thinking that you’d be pinching him if you said this while you were awake, and better yet sober. he can’t resist just carding his hand through your hair and rubbing at that spot in your neck, not resisting to take a picture of his lovie who’d be laughing with a migraine by the next morning.

“but m’still gonna try and make it less horrid for you.”

summary: THIRD TIME LUCKY HOPEFULLY 🤞🏼 (I blame my tumblr not you ❤️) gang!Harry meets a&e doctor y/n for the first time after a fight...
question: THIRD TIME LUCKY HOPEFULLY 🤞🏼 (I blame my tumblr not you ❤️) gang!Harry meets a&e doctor y/n for the first time after a fight and he’s a little drunk and keeps rambling about how beautiful he thinks she is???  I also love you and your writing 💜💜💜
answer:
baby, do you know that video with a baby being grumpy at first to his doctor but eventually, he gets so awed by her that while she puts the stethoscope on his lil chest,, he leans his head onto her arm??

THAT’S EXACTLY GANG!HARRY WOULD DO!!!! would be a lil drunk but not drunk enough to not be aware of what’s happening, even the antiseptic that stings being dabbed onto his skin after the disinfectant that hurt just as much. would be aware of it all yet it just seems like that the little shots of tequila made him have no filter.

“t-thank you, l-lovie.”

he’d hiccup throughout while he’s watching you, an angel as he figures, who’s in the form of a doctor slightly grimace because every time his body racks with his hiccups, the more painful the stitching would be.

“gonna get a nurse to get y’some water, harry — and you’re gonna drink it all, alright?”

he’s managed to introduce himself throughout which makes his name roll of your tongue easily, as if you’e known him for ages and that makes him grin, even if there’s a needle and thread working on the inside part of his arm.

harry nods earnestly as he understands, muttering a soft little “m’kay” as you adjust him and his arm once again so it would be easier for the both of you, his lips pouting as he just yawns, looking at you with an adorable little smile.

“you’re an angel — even if y’poking me with a needle.”
